application

Class Client_GUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Client_GUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GUI_Interface_Client

    public class Client_GUI
extends java.lang.Object
implements GUI_Interface_Client
    This is the GUI used with the client part of the chat. It implements GUI_Interface_Client class witch makes it compatible with the Client class The overridden methods is used by the Client class to controll the GUI.
    Author:
    Fredrik Johansson, Matias Edin
